Hi Brad

Thanks for spending time with me yesterday.  After our discussion I thought about the role and the implications of a move to the USA.  I also discussed the opportunity with my husband, John Bergman.  We ended up with some questions which I detail below.  

1.	Please provide more detail about the remit of the role (I can speak to Savita to get this if you wish).

2.	Would I be able to make changes in the structure of the team?

3.	What is the timeline for the transition period?

4.	How long would you expect this assignment to last?

5.	What happens when the assignment comes to an end - would I be offered a position in the European office again?

6.	Would Enron be prepared to locate an appropriate role for my husband?  I attach his resume below.

7.	Would Enron arrange visas for my husband and myself?

8.	What type of package would be offered for the relocation etc.?

I look forward to hearing from you.  I am under some time pressure at the moment - I need to have resolution asap.

